      "tAsideSectionIntroductionLabel01": "Introduction",
      "tAsideSectionIntroductionDescription01": "In the wake of the successful launch of AngelAi, it became apparent that we needed an in-house solution for document signing to further streamline our operations. Enter AiSign, a groundbreaking platform designed to revolutionize document signing processes, freeing us from reliance on third-party services like DocuSign. With AiSign, we embarked on a journey to empower users with a seamless, secure, and efficient document signing experience, integrated seamlessly with AngelAi.",
      "tAsideSectionProblemLabel01": "Problem",
      "tAsideSectionProblemDescription01": "Despite the success of our flagship product, AngelAi, our reliance on third-party document signing services like DocuSign posed several challenges. These services were costly, lacked customization options, and did not fully align with our vision of seamless integration within our ecosystem. Recognizing the need for a proprietary solution, management tasked me and two other developers with the AiSign project to address these pain points and elevate our operations to the next level.",
