      "tAsideSectionIntroductionLabel02": "Introduction",
      "tAsideSectionIntroductionDescription02": "As a key member of the AngelAi team, I spearheaded the integration of property listings into our AI platform. AiListings emerged as a groundbreaking addition, harnessing the power of AI to transform the property search experience. Our goal was to create a seamless interface between homebuyers, realtors, and property data, revolutionizing how individuals discover their dream homes.",
      "tAsideSectionProblemLabel02": "Problem",
      "tAsideSectionProblemDescription02": "Despite AngelAi's success, we recognized the need to enhance its capabilities by incorporating real-time property listings. Our challenge lay in providing enough value to realtors that they would want to list their properties through AngelAi. Reaching this goal and getting plenty of listings across the United States would provide us with a large database of active listings that would allow our users to search for their dream home without having to leave AngelAi.",
      "tAsideSectionActionLabel02": "Action",
      "tAsideSectionActionDescription02": "To tackle these challenges, I led the implementation of a Node.js middleware solution, collaborating closely with sysadmins to set up deployment strategies, and establish maintenance processes. This approach was preferable to rewriting an existing website in NextJs to provide the same SEO content without having web crawlers execute client side javascript as required by React-Helmet. Additionally, the AI had to be configured to recognize addresses, compare a given address against our database, fetch the record and provide the listing to the user. The React client for AngelAi had to be configured to allow iframes to expose the sister property listings website and allow the user to access all of the required information from within AngelAi.",
