      "tAsideSectionIntroductionLabel10": "Introduction",
      "tAsideSectionIntroductionDescription10": "Callouts Evolved aims to break language barriers and communication restrictions in video games, envisioning a future where gamers of all languages and abilities can seamlessly communicate. From Brazilian Sign Language to English, our platform ensures inclusivity and accessibility in gaming interactions.",
