      "tAsideSectionIntroductionLabel11": "Introduction",
      "tAsideSectionIntroductionDescription11": "In response to the ever-changing landscape of technology, I built getDevNews() to provide a single source for professional developers to keep up with important industry news. Our goal was simple: to become the primary destination for developers seeking the latest industry insights, trends, and updates.",
      "tAsideSectionProblemLabel11": "Problem",
      "tAsideSectionProblemDescription11": "With the vast amount of information available online, professional developers often struggled to keep pace with the latest news relevant to their field, and new developers have trouble differentiating between advertisements, the new hype, and actual industry trends. Existing news aggregation platforms lacked the specificity and depth required for developers, leading to information overload and inefficiency.",
      "tAsideSectionActionLabel11": "Action",
      "tAsideSectionActionDescription11": "Recognizing the need for a tailored solution, I developed and deployed an MVP for getDevNews in 5 working days and iterated the site based on user feedback to ensure that the site was delivering the news developers wanted in a timely manner. The initial design was based on the Drudge Report, but as many developers are visual, the need to display thumbnails was predicted and adjusted for. After the initial launch, the database was tuned to resubscribe to specific channels to allow for real-time news tracking, and RSS feeds were tuned to provide the information developers need from trusted sources. The last 24 hours of news is available to the public without needing to sign in. Users are able to sign in via magic link. Once signed in, they can either pay a subscription to hide ads or pay to have ads showcased on the site, after approval by admin.",
      "tAsideSectionResultsLabel11": "Results",
      "tAsideSectionResultsDescription11": "Get Dev News quickly gained traction within the developer community, establishing itself as the go-to source for daily news. We witnessed explosive growth in new and recurring users, and have plans underway for further enhancements and expansion. This success reaffirmed the importance of tailored solutions in meeting the unique needs of the target audience.",
